    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-quality condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and free of any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly impeccable example of engineering excellence.",
